{"tid":806129,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★支童玩「食雞」後跳樓亡　母親：要告到遊戲公司破產","createTime":"2018-09-04T11:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T10:03:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":45,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d151cd5ead6c2747bde81df92ecb456de8cca9c8","tid":806129,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T11:55:40.000Z","msg":"中國江蘇省有一名 13 歲男童日前於親戚家跳樓身亡，他的母親指兒子生前正在玩稱「吃雞」的遊戲《絕地求生》（PUBG），更認定他是模仿遊戲動作，認為跳樓不會致命，因而釀成悲劇，更憤而表示「要告到它（開發商）破產」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/3532822.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F3532822.jpg&h=439fe5f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據中國媒體《江西新聞網》報道，涉事男童名叫徐天賜，來自江蘇海門市，家中環境富裕，因雙親長年於南非經商，平日寄住在親友家中。據報道， 8 月 29 日深夜 11 時左右，他與同學正在玩《絕地求生》，但直到隔天凌晨，他突然從 4 樓一躍而下，當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n徐天賜的母親表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">兒子人見人愛</span>，根本沒有自殺的理由。更推斷兒子的死與《絕地求生》有直接關係，「我兒子絕對是遊戲害死的，沒有其他原因的」，因為在遊戲中角色從高處跳下，只會出一點血，並不會致命。所以兒子才模仿遊戲跳樓。她更堅稱，兒子是因為遊戲而死，所以要告到遊戲公司破產，賠光用別人生命賺來的錢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/09/04/jump-after-play-pubg/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2Fjump-after-play-pubg%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=mC2PSn5UZ7EsjR9XJG2kFJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=6eec01e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/09/04/jump-after-play-pubg/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"a9fc4d0af6079fddb94635a784b83f550c880168","tid":806129,"uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T11:55:48.000Z","msg":"兒子人見人愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ad95ee895bcc1ab358b8120977c81b75e52674","tid":806129,"uid":156737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20